大堆，即所有的节点都大于等于或着小于等于它的每个子节点</li></ul>`,25),h=n("div",{class:"language-javascript line-numbers-mode","data-ext":"js","data-title":"js"},[n("pre",{class:"language-javascript"},[n("code",null,[n("span",{class:"token keyword"},"class"),s(),n("span",{class:"token class-name"},"MinHeap"),s(),n("span",{class:"token punctuation"},"{"),s(`
